---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
    title="EHS - Environmental, Health & Safety"
    description="Overview of T-Vetas Network's EHS program"
    lang="en"
>
    <section class="ehs-section">
        <h1>Environmental, Health & Safety</h1>
        <p>
            T-Vetas Network places great emphasis on occupational safety. We maintain comprehensive guidelines and regular training to keep all staff safe on site.<br>
            We believe <strong>Work Safely, Return Safely</strong> is fundamental and continually strengthen on-site management and awareness.
        </p>
    </section>

    <section class="ehs-section policy-section">
        <h1>Corporate Social Responsibility & EHS Policy</h1>
        <div>
            <p>
                <strong>Business Ethics</strong><br>We operate with integrity and protect confidential information.
            </p>
            <p>
                <strong>Employee Rights</strong><br>We comply with compensation laws and prohibit child labor.
            </p>
            <p>
                <strong>EHS Commitment</strong><br>We strive for zero accidents through regular training and continual improvement.
            </p>
        </div>
        <div class="policy-image-download">
            <a href="/ehs-policy_zhtw.pdf" class="policy-download" download>Download EHS Policy Statement PDF</a>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="ehs-section">
        <h1>Key EHS Documents and Guidelines</h1>
        <ul class="ehs-doc-list">
            <li>EHS Manual for Contractors</li>
            <li>Emergency Action Plan</li>
            <li>Hazard Identification and Risk Assessment</li>
            <li>Lockout/Tagout Procedures</li>
            <li>Tool Safety and PPE</li>
            <li>Fire Safety and Extinguisher Guide</li>
            <li>Work at Height & Fall Prevention</li>
            <li>Daily Hazard Notification</li>
            <li>Incident Investigation & Records</li>
            <li>Electrical Safety & Grounding Guide</li>
            <li>MEWP Operation Regulation</li>
            <li>Stop Work Authority</li>
            <li>Subcontractor Safety Management</li>
        </ul>
        <p>
            These documents cover on-site work, equipment operation, emergency response and incident investigation to ensure everyone follows standard procedures and stays safe.
        </p>
        <p>
            For more details please <a href="/en/about#contact" class="vendor-link">contact us</a>.
        </p>
    </section>
</Layout>

<style>
.ehs-section {
    max-width: 900px;
    margin: 2rem auto;
    padding: 2rem 1.5rem;
    background: #fff;
    border-radius: 10px;
    box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.06);
}
.policy-section {
    background: #f7fafc;
    border-left: 4px solid #44B3FF;
    margin-top: 0;
}
.policy-image-download {
    text-align: center;
    margin: 2rem 0 0 0;
}
.policy-img {
    max-width: 350px;
    width: 100%;
    margin: 0 auto 1rem;
    display: block;
    border: 1px solid #eee;
    border-radius: 6px;
    box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.04);
}
.policy-download {
    display: inline-block;
    margin-top: 0.5rem;
    padding: 0.5em 1.2em;
    background: #44B3FF;
    color: #fff;
    border-radius: 4px;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: bold;
    transition: background 0.2s;
}
.policy-download:hover {
    background: #FF7A00;
}
.ehs-doc-list {
    margin: 1.5rem 0;
    padding-left: 1.2rem;
}
.ehs-doc-list li {
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
}
.ehs-section h1 {
    font-size: 2rem;
    font-weight: bold;
    margin-bottom: 1.2rem;
    color: #1A2A47;
    text-align: center;
}
.vendor-link {
    color: #44B3FF;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: color 0.2s;
}

.vendor-link:hover {
    color: #FF7A00;
    text-decoration: underline;
}
</style>